author: SupraDarky

text: I've had this song stuck in my head for a while now and since I didn't want to be alone, here it is for you guys. Someone actually gifted me this game on Steam (thanks!), I played and finished it yesterday. It's hard to call it a game though, it feels more like a prototype. You basically get money out of burning things, so you can then buy more things to burn from a catalogue. Seeing what each toy does and finding combos is the best part (and this theme), but it can get boring after a while.
